{"tid":810224,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"爭幾萬卡數，想做結餘轉户","createTime":"2018-09-07T18:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T03:20:26.000Z","uid":6169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82bf38db62cff4cbcb14e7832292e3b619b1fce7","tid":810224,"uid":6169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:37:59.000Z","msg":"爭緊幾萬卡數，話多唔多話少唔少<br />\n但都夠我有排煩<br />\n<br />\n最近睇到可以試下做結餘轉户<br />\n想咋咋林清咗啲卡數，最少比少好多息先<br />\n但頭先又見到有巴打話: on9先做結餘轉户<br />\n<br />\n咁其實即係好定唔好？做咗會唔會影響信貸評級？點先影響到個信貸評級？邊間做會好啲？如果唔能夠準時還咁會點？<br />\n<br />\n突然煩到瞓唔著，求救下各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64bf0d82221667ff8a424d1fd2a7391d08f372b","tid":810224,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"其實轉左咪都係要還嗰個數<br />\n係你換咗個債主"},{"pid":"efb6d1a68c664b8266dd576fd89953f4fe31ae62","tid":810224,"uid":6169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64bf0d82221667ff8a424d1fd2a7391d08f372b","tid":810224,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"其實轉左咪都係要還嗰個數<br />\n係你換咗個債主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"我明，但如果我準時還，係咪真係減到好多利息先？"},{"pid":"96be4a2062e0ca2063f3e8e653e18e0b9f0ba629","tid":810224,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efb6d1a68c664b8266dd576fd89953f4fe31ae62","tid":810224,"uid":6169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b64bf0d82221667ff8a424d1fd2a7391d08f372b","tid":810224,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"其實轉左咪都係要還嗰個數<br />\n係你換咗個債主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"我明，但如果我準時還，係咪真係減到好多利息先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T18:44:26.000Z","msg":"但同時 你張信用卡都會自由返<br />\n你有冇信心唔會繼續用多啲錢先<br />\n<br />\n最後愈還愈多"},{"pid":"7b2ae400b195e390fed21303f895fa5af23f8e88","tid":810224,"uid":41368,"like":0,"